{"tid":382161,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Minecraft\u0010] 24小時休閒生存伺服器 開心版/正版 無白名單 慢生活","createTime":"2017-08-31T13:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T10:12:00.000Z","uid":53970,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"09e7421be38f864f37fc5864d4f4458d8415536c","tid":382161,"uid":53970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:27:50.000Z","msg":"Minecraft 生存 Server<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">簡介</span></span><br />\n依個SER既主題同玩法係Relaxing Survival , 簡單, 休閒, 輕鬆, 生存。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主張多人互動世界，大家一齊玩，一齊起屋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">規則</span></span><br />\n1：開心遊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">生存世界設定&amp;插件&amp;指令</span></span><br />\n防creeper爆 <br />\n可以SET兩個HOME (例如: /sethome abc 之後 /home abc 就OK)<br />\n有領地插件 (名：GriefPrevention)<br />\n/back<br />\nLift 升降機 (需準備 鐵磚1粒,木牌數個,制數粒 黎SET一部升降機)<br />\n/co i (查看物品被破壞或被偷竊記錄)<br />\n/mutechat (見到打字頻道好煩, 可以MUTE左佢)<br />\n木牌鎖箱或鎖門 (如果想朋友都可以用到你鎖左既箱或門, 右click個木牌打/lockette 3 朋友名)<br />\nMoney系統 (/bal 或 /money可以check自己有幾多錢, 錢可以換貨幣同玩家交易個時用，有商店)<br />\n/hat (將手上面既物品笠係個頭度做裝飾)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">購物教學</span></span><br />\n左圖: 將你身上64個黑曜石轉做$3200<br />\n右圖: 你用$50購買1粒黑曜石<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/64ex970n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F64ex970n&h=623c0007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">加入方法</span></span><br />\nWalkin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  /register [password]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ip</span></span>: kinglam.mcph.eu<br />\n<br />\n舊POST 5: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/302902/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/302902/page/1</a><br />\n舊POST 4: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/204927/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/204927/page/1</a><br />\n舊POST 3: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/165476/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/165476/page/1</a><br />\n舊POST 2: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/124427/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/124427/page/1</a><br />\n舊POST 1: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/101334/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/101334/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7450093a534ce0d7f6a50b75637becc7d81550b1","tid":382161,"uid":53970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:32:21.000Z","msg":"些少之前整落嘅pixel art 歡迎同好一齊整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V5PF4ao.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV5PF4ao.png&h=ccf1eec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6474980.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6474980.png&h=c0374b2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd38900ab7e4a4f4add3b0d7b282fed9d6be9266","tid":382161,"uid":53970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:34:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">有Discord</span>：<a href=\"https://discord.gg/t9yDcvG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2Ft9yDcvG&d=S%2Fm%2BpYT8BQieyvnJORc5ZL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=654c93a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/t9yDcvG</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br 