 (<span style=\"color: green;\">教學:</span> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qxUPo3Dm5L8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqxUPo3Dm5L8&d=S%2Fm%2BpYT8BQieyvnJORc5ZL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=82669d4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qxUPo3Dm5L8</a> )"},{"pid":"25ee88767d67ccaadd7b73778b6a14e16abf66dd","tid":382161,"uid":51592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:31:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ea4c462dc4ccb763fcebaa1693fe8864360789","tid":382161,"uid":21749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:26:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>Relaxing Survival Server (小型生存)</em> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">IP:</span></span> kinglam.mcph.eu<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">特色玩法 (9/2017版本):</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">24</span></span>小時開放, <span style=\"color: red;\">無白名單</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">正版</span> 或 <span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開心版</span></span> 可一同進場<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">火會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燃燒</span></span>, TNT可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">炸爛野</span></span></span>, <span style=\"color: green;\">CREEPER唔會<br />\n</span><span style=\"color: teal;\">有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">領地插件</span></span>, 保護家園 (教學係1樓)<br />\n已內置<span style=\"color: maroon;\">自動清除紅石連閃</span>功能<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">唯一管理員</span>, 不會影響玩家進行遊戲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無規則</span>, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">自由奔放無拘無束</span></span></span>, <span style=\"color: green;\">只要唔玩死SERVER, 做乜都可以</span> <span style=\"color: teal;\">(舊POST規則已不適用)<br />\n</span>有<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">線上地圖</span></span>, 方便偵察<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">有創造世界</span>, 每人可領取一塊100X100有保護既地入面用Creative Mode砌野<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">小型商店 (可以換錢的物品有: 黑曜石, 地獄石, CD, 不死圖騰)<br />\n簡單副本 (可刷 不死圖騰, 史萊姆球)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">一般指令</span></span><br />\n/sethome 可以設置<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">2</span></span>個家<br />\n/home 回家<br />\n/back 返回上一次死亡 / 傳送的位置<br />\n/tpa  傳送到其他玩家的位置<br />\n/hat  將手上的東西放在頭上, 可解除綁定詛咒<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">/co i  查看被破壞的記錄</span>, <span style=\"color: maroon;\">然後去<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋仇</span></span></span><br />\n/mutechat 關閉文字頻道<br />\n/bal      查看身上擁有的money<br />\n /money 查看身上擁有的money<br />\n /help   查看其他可用的指令<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">希望入黎玩既玩家都可以開心遊玩~<span style=\"color: violet;\">❤</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">IP:</span></span> kinglam.mcph.eu"},{"pid":"37634ef0b79b1435624b3f1da770393b2113b730","tid":382161,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:02:13.000Z","msg":"❤"},{"pid":"53befaaf4cacb8a7a15837b1e24d267568e3227f","tid":382161,"uid":21749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:54:14.000Z","msg":"今日下午受到大量流動IP開心版小號洗登入登出,<br />\n導致server出現lag既情況, 而加開返白名單, 但其他所有既setting無變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想加入既新玩家, <br />\n可以係post度留game名 或 <br />\n入Discord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/t9yDcvG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2Ft9yDcvG&d=S%2Fm%2BpYT8BQieyvnJORc5ZL%